section_title: EVENT ON QUANTIFIED ECONOMY-WIDE EMISSION REDUCTION TARGETS BY DEVELOPED COUNTRIES :
sentences: Barbara Muik, UNFCCC Secretariat, presented a technical paper based on developed countries submissions.

She noted clarity on some of the elements, but that there is uncertainty on, inter alia : the role of LULUCF and carbon credits from market-based mechanisms, as well as on whether conditions and assumptions attached to the pledges are met.
